    {
      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "Wrap up warmly and naturally using their first name if you have it.\n\nUse {{current_time}} to choose the appropriate greeting:\n- Before 12:00 PM: \"Have a wonderful morning!\"\n- 12:00 PM to 5:00 PM: \"Have a wonderful afternoon!\"\n- After 5:00 PM: \"Have a wonderful evening!\"\n\nSay something like: \"Thanks so much for calling Premier MD, {{first_name}}! Have a wonderful [morning/afternoon/evening]!\"\n\nKeep it brief — one or two sentences max. Don't ask any more questions."
      },
