      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "Ask for the caller's date of birth.\n\nSay something like: \"And could I get your date of birth?\"\n\nConfirmation — only when needed:\n- If the date was clearly stated and sounds plausible (e.g. \"January 14th, 1984\"), accept it without repeating.\n- If the date was unclear, mumbled, or only partially given, ask them to repeat it.\n\nAccept any reasonable spoken format (e.g. \"March 5th, 1990\", \"oh three oh five ninety\", \"three five ninety\")."
      }
