      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "The date of birth needs clarification. The issue is: {{dob_error}}\n\nIf {{dob_clarification_reason}} is \"ambiguous_month_day\":\n  Read back both possible interpretations and ask which\n  one is correct.\n  Example: \"Just to make sure — did you mean October 12th\n  or December 10th?\"\n\nOtherwise, relay the clarification issue naturally —\ndon't read the error word for word."
